title: Asset Listing: Add $PAXG on ETH v1
body:
Asset Listing: Add $PAXG on ETH v1

Intro: This is a vote to list $PAXG on ETH v1 with a collateral factor and collateral cap.

Proposal: https://forum.cream.finance/t/proposal-paxos-gold-paxg-listing/1674

Rationale: List $PAXG on ETH v1 market with collateral factor of 60% and collateral cap of $1M. C.R.E.A.M. will be the first money market to list PAXG.

For:
List $PAXG on ETH v1 market with Collateral Factor: 60% and Collateral Cap: $1M.

Against:
Do nothing.
author: 0xd662fA474C0A1346a26374bb4581D1F6D3Fb2d94
